- We've been waiting for you.

663
00:34:40,980 --> 00:34:41,820
This time,

664
00:34:42,020 --> 00:34:43,060
who would've thought

665
00:34:43,540 --> 00:34:46,500
the people of Yuncui City were so united?

666
